{"tid":1190840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方可遠距離監控得知遊行人士的個人資料","createTime":"2019-06-07T14:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T15:34:29.000Z","uid":205253,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"667eff76d1f9732d3b57e5695ff03d931a11b457","tid":1190840,"uid":205253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"有一樣野大家好少提！！！好少有人關注！！！<br />\n<br />\n所有用新身份證 請留意<br />\n<br />\n新身份證附有RFID功能　惹監控疑慮<br />\n<br />\n令人關注的是，晶片將具RFID(Radio-frequency identification)通訊功能，政府稱為「支援無線傳輸技術界面」，將不須直接碰觸讀卡器。政府早前已就此新功能「放風」，引來網民、社運界極大反響。通常擔心政府可以用新身份證來「隔空抄牌」，例如以器械掌握所有出席市民的身份。<br />\n<br />\n政府計劃將新一代智能身份證加入RFID（無線傳輸）技術，有市民憂慮個人資料安全問題，警方今後能夠「隔空抄牌」，在市民不知情下讀取其個人資料。《壹錘定音》主持李慧玲訪問了RFID專家，分析RFID的種種，並親身測試其隔空讀取資料的技術。<br />\n<br />\n於科技公司任職高層的RFID專家謝小江表示，RFID系統可讀取資料的範圍，取決於接收器和晶片，根據國際標準，若採用高頻率(UltraHighFrequency)系統，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可讀取範圍可達10米</span>，帶電池的「主動式RFID」<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">讀取範圍更可達100米</span>。但如果像八達通採用的系統，接收範圍超出1米已超出國際標準。<br />\n<br />\n慧玲拿著謝先生提供的RFID標籤，親身測試隔空讀取資料的技術，結果顯示一部電腦熒幕大小的接收器，可以讀取4至5米範圍內的RFID標籤。<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20150121&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=53355070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20150121%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D53355070&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=ee9454ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20150121%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D53355070&h=e922f396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20150121&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=53355070</a><br />\n<br />\n當年好地地無啦啦要換新身分證，仲要加入RFID功能已經好令人懷疑。<br />\n<br />\n保險起見<br />\n用新身份證可以用<br />\n<br />\n用防rfid 卡套（最建議）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VGkLsvO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVGkLsvO.png&h=dcfcbcb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自制錫紙卡套<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4k1iNuX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4k1iNuX.png&h=6bf299b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n只要把卡放進錫紙製成卡套，就可以令RFID技術失效。經過測試，錫紙能夠成功阻隔RFID技術。不過錫紙易爛，所以要經常更換。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自制金屬保護層<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8m8UkP1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8m8UkP1.png&h=f08d80ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n在銀包的外層，放入金屬保護層。先量度銀包的闊及深，然後在白紙上剪下相應的尺寸。再把錫箔黏貼紙，貼在紙上。最後把成品放進銀包就可以了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/200383/%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3%E6%96%B0%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AD%89%E9%9A%B1%E6%86%82-%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A04%E6%8B%9B%E9%98%B2rfid/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F200383%2F%25E6%258B%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E9%259A%25B1%25E6%2586%2582-%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25BD%25A04%25E6%258B%259B%25E9%2598%25B2rfid%2F2&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=af01c384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/200383/%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3%E6%96%B0%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AD%89%E9%9A%B1%E6%86%82-%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A04%E6%8B%9B%E9%98%B2rfid/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3mZDNxd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3mZDNxd.gif&h=8d70ce40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39c8d735c47bce05bf371a5067773f4b09e71369","tid":1190840,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T14:35:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c59bbe954d27938b3dd91b0dfcb8286409c2ca75","tid":1190840,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T14:37:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df8c0f77a245ba472a340a5f9c76b10912533831","tid":1190840,"uid":41784,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"39c8d735c47bce05bf371a5067773f4b09e71369","tid":1190840,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T14:35:39.000Z","msg":